  ('pukao-acfc4025-moex-00007', 'pukao-acfc4025', 'pukao-acfc4025-moex-114-156cbda0', 'sub-pukao-acfc4025-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關在作業系統中，下列敘述何者正確？', '["行程（Process）可能處於非活躍（Inactive）狀態，直到作業系統重新啟動", "作業（Job）在變成程序（Process）之前，可能會處於保留（Hold）或被結束（Terminated）的狀態", "程序（Process）只能處於就緒（Ready）或執行中（Running）兩種狀態之中", "程式（Program）是靜態的可執行檔案，作業系統執行後，會立刻成為程序（Process）"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:35:39+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ebba180acb37", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b58c95b8bfaa", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114080", "c": "446", "s": "2504", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "計算機概要", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "pukao", "civil_category": "電子工程"}'::jsonb, NULL),
